high_descs: Turn right to face the cutting board over the sink.
Pick up the knife from the left edge of the cutting board.
Turn around and go the the counter that is to the right of the stove.
Slice the cabbage that is on the counter.
Put the knife down near the front of the counter, parallel to the front edge.
Pick up the nearest slice of cabbage.
Turn left and go to the door, then turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the cabbage slice near the front of the middle shelf and close the fridge, then take the cabbage back out of the fridge and re-close the door.
Turn around to your left and go to the counter at the left of the stove.
Place the cabbage slice in the middle of the counter space in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold slice of cabbage on the counter in front of the toaster.

high_descs: Go forward, and turn to the sink on your right
Pick up the knife that's in front of you
Turn around and go to the counter space to the right of the stove
Cut the lettuce that's in the back corner
Put the knife down in front of you, on the counter
Pick up the closest piece of lettuce
Turn to your left and go to the fridge
Open the fridge and put the piece of lettuce on the second shelf of the fridge, close the door and wait, then open it again and take out the lettuce
Turn to your left and go over to the counter space, on the left of the stove
Place the lettuce down on the counter on the right side of the bread
anns.task_desc: Cut a piece of lettuce, chill it, place it next to a loaf of bread

high_descs: Walk towards the wall and turn to the right facing the cutting board
Pick up a knife on the counter
With the knife, turn to the left and go towards the stove
Using the knife slice the head of lettuce next to the egg
Set down the knife on the counter
Pick up a slice of the lettuce
Turn to the left and walk towards the door, at the door turn left and open the fridge door
Put the lettuce in the fridge, close the door, then open the door and take the lettuce out again
Close the fridge door, turn left and walk towards the stove
Put the lettuce on the counter next to the toaster
anns.task_desc: Slice a piece of lettuce, chill it in the fridge, set it next to the toaster
